			<item>
				<title>Privacy Policy</title>
				<link>https://embetter.in/privacy/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
				<guid>https://embetter.in/privacy/</guid>
				<description>&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Information We Collect&lt;/strong&gt; – We collect only the information necessary to provide our services, such as contact details and project requirements.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Client Data Privacy&lt;/strong&gt; – All client data, including project specifications, business information, and communications, is kept strictly private.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Intellectual Property Confidentiality&lt;/strong&gt; – Any source code, designs, or deliverables shared with or created for the client are treated as confidential and will not be disclosed.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;No Third-Party Sharing&lt;/strong&gt; – We do not sell, share, or transfer client data or project-related information to any third parties for processing or any other purpose.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>Refund Policy</title>
				<link>https://embetter.in/refund/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
				<guid>https://embetter.in/refund/</guid>
				<description>&lt;ol&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advance Payments&lt;/strong&gt; – All advance payments made toward a project are non-refundable, as they secure project commencement and resource allocation.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Milestone Payments&lt;/strong&gt; – Payments made upon completion of a milestone are non-refundable, as the work has been delivered and accepted.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Third-Party Expenses&lt;/strong&gt; – Any amounts paid toward third-party services, tools, APIs, or infrastructure on behalf of the client are non-refundable.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Valid Refund Scenarios&lt;/strong&gt; – In any other valid scenario where a refund is applicable, the refund will be processed within 15 working days from the date of approval.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
			<item>
				<title>Terms and Conditions</title>
				<link>https://embetter.in/terms/</link>
				<pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:00:00 +0530</pubDate>
				<guid>https://embetter.in/terms/</guid>
				<description>&lt;p&gt;These terms govern the services provided by &lt;strong&gt;Embetter Technologies Pvt Ltd&lt;/strong&gt; to the client.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Scope of Work&lt;/strong&gt; – Work is limited to the agreed scope in the proposal. Any changes or additions require a written change order and may affect timeline and cost.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Client Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt; – The client must provide timely feedback, approvals, access, and materials. Delays caused by the client may push the project timeline and are not the responsibility of Embetter.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
			</item>
